Adrar Aberkan neɣ mintinigru (s Tutlayt Taṣirbit: Црна Гора/Crna Gora) tga tamurt tezga deg unẓul n [[turuft]]. tga yiwet seg snat temura   tamunt n ṣirbya. g 21 mayyu 2006 yella ustay n ubeṭṭu ɣef [[ṣirbya]] , yebɣa ugar n 55.5% n inamuren [[azarug]].
tiweḍ tejumma n Muntinigru nig n 13812 km² , uṭṭun n imzdaɣen nnes nig n 650,000 n ufgan، tamaẓunt isem nnes budguritsa .
adrar aberkan iga yiwen seg tigdudayin n yuguslafya tamaynut، deffir ma zzurgen xef w-amun ayuguslavi amezwaru kkuẓ seg sḍiṣt tgdudayin ، jar aseggas 1991 d 1992 ،. Yella ubeṛraḥ s uzarug n temurt g wass n 3 yunyu 2006.

